&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="http://cixar.comhttp://cixar.com/~kris.kowal/bdoc/program/backdrop/"&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Tomorrow's project is adjusting the linear gradients that overlay the cells in the foreground terrain to catch the light of the sun, moon, sky, or form shadows and silhouettes.&lt;/p&gt;
